title: Murray's Money
description:
Mina Kimes and Frank Isola discuss if Kyler Murray is worth the huge 5-year contract extension he and the Cardinals agreed to, if it is a mistake for the Browns to pass on trading for Jimmy Garoppolo and how the Sixers should feel about Harden’s new contract.
